metadata.name: CardArtMillionaireMaker
metadata.description: This is a lucky collection of playing cards. This is your chance to be a part of the growing CardArtMillionaireMaker community. Along with the lucky community members that are able to be a part of this release we are airdropping 200 ETH to the valued user who mints the Laser Eye Queen of Hearts. We will also be air dropping 20 ETH to the user holding the standard Queen of Hearts. Once all of the cards are in play we will reveal your lucky card!
